e (filtered) tasks\n- User can apply bulk complete, bulk delete, or bulk priority change to selected tasks\n- After deleting tasks, a toast appears: \"3 tasks deleted\" with an \"Undo\" button\n- Clicking \"Undo\" within 5 seconds restores the deleted tasks\n- `Ctrl+Z` (or `Cmd+Z`) undoes the last action; `Ctrl+Shift+Z` (or `Cmd+Shift+Z`) redoes\n- Undo/redo works for add, delete, complete, edit, and reorder operations\n- Undo history is limited to the last 50 actions to bound memory usage\n- Toast notifications stack and auto-dismiss after 5 seconds unless hovered\n- Searching while offline works against the local IndexedDB store\n- Bulk operations use a single API call for efficiency\n\n### Technical Notes\n- Use a command pattern for undo/redo: each action stores a `do` and `undo` operation\n- Bulk operations should use a single API call: `POST /api/v1/todos/bulk` with `{ action, ids, payload? }`\n- Toast notifications should use portal rendering to avoid layout interference\n- Use `zustand/middleware` to implement the undo/redo middleware cleanly\n- Debounce search input by 150ms to avoid excessive filtering\n\n---\n\n## Sprint 10: E2E Tests, Final Polish & Documentation\n\n### Scope\n- Write Playwright E2E tests for all critical user flows\n- Full accessibility audit and fixes (screen reader, keyboard, ARIA)\n- Add onboarding experience for first-time users\n- Add data export/import (JSON)\n- Final cross-browser testing and bug fixes\n- Write user-facing documentation\n\n### Deliverables\n- `frontend/e2e/todo-crud.spec.ts` — CRUD flow tests\n- `frontend/e2e/drag-reorder.spec.ts` — Drag-and-drop tests\n- `frontend/e2e/offline-sync.spec.ts` — Offline mode and sync tests\n- `frontend/e2e/filters-search.spec.ts` — Filter and search tests\n- `frontend/e2e/theme-a11y.spec.ts` — Theme toggle and accessibility tests\n- `frontend/src/components/Onboarding.tsx` — First-run walkthrough\n- `frontend/src/utils/exportImport.ts` — JSON export/import functions\n- `frontend/src